# Skills and manifests are synced into this agent's .github/ from the
# repository-root .github/ by deploy.sh (sync_github_assets). The root repo is
# the single source of truth; these copies exist only so the Dockerfile can
# bundle them into the hosted-agent image (COPY . user_agent/). Never commit
# them here — they would duplicate the root tree and drift.
.github/skills/
.github/manifests/
queries/
config.json.template
config.json